sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Creation of an Executable by an Executable
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the creation of an executable by another executable

mitre_attack_techniques.signature_description: Stores files to the Windows startup directory
Creates a start menu entry (Start Menu\\Programs\\Startup)
Drops PE files to the user directory
Creates files inside the user directory
Drops PE files to the user root directory (C:\\Documents and Settings\\User or C:\\Users\\User)
May sleep (evasive loops) to hinder dynamic analysis
Queries the volume information (name, serial number etc) of a device
Uses HTTPS for network communication, use the SSL MITM Proxy cookbook for further analysis
